Any Tax Revenue? 



What if Smart Stop were no longer here? And the money put back where it came from?



What about More At Four?  MAF does not help day cares, and Does it really help children? 

 MAF TOOK children from TAX paying day care and put them into a program that generates NO TAX Revenue.

Again. Who is MAF benefiting?  Public Schools, Head Start. Neither of which pay TAXES, Local or State.

If the money was put in DSS subsidy, Robeson County would not have 1200 children on a DSS Waiting List.



