Currently, we have 7 full time children, and 13 after-school kids. We have 2 full time (one of which is me) and 1 part-time employee. 7 or 8 years ago we had 9 employees and around 50 children.



We have to pay Local, State, Unemployment( that has skyrocketed, and of NO FAULT of day cares, NAFTA), Federal Taxes. We get NO tax breaks or incentives from no one. 



 If small businesses are the backbone of our economy, why is it that everybody is trying to break it?



